LLM_response_editer_en:
In order to complete the current subtask "Double click to open Microsoft Edge browser", you need to move the mouse pointer to the icon of Microsoft Edge browser and perform the double click operation. According to the icon position in the screen image, the following are the corresponding JSON operations:```json
[
    {"action_type": "MouseAction", "mouse_action_type": "double_click", "mouse_button": "left", "mouse_position": {"width": 50, "height": 135}}
]
```These values are estimated based on the approximate position of the icon on the screen. In actual operation, you may need to fine tune according to the exact position of the icon.
